title: Hard Disk Sentinel Pro v4.00 Multilingual  MPT
description:
Hard Disk Sentinel (HDSentinel) is a multi-OS SSD and HDD
monitoring and analysis software. Its goal is to find, test,
diagnose and repair hard disk drive problems, report and display
SSD and HDD health, performance degradations and failures. Hard
Disk Sentinel gives complete textual description, tips and
displays/reports the most comprehensive information about the hard
disks and solid state disks inside the computer and in external
enclosures (USB / e-SATA). Many different alerts and report
options are available to ensure maximum safety of your valuable
